
'''* The Birth of Impersonal Exchange: The Community Responsibility System and Impartial Justice. Avner Greif.'''

URL = http://www.stanford.edu/~avner/Greif_Papers/2006%20JEP%20The%20Birth%20of%20Impersonal%20Exchange.pdf


=Description=

"By fostering impersonal exchange and institutional development, the community
responsibility system laid the basis for its own replacement by overarching systems of
law-based exchange. Long-distance trade led to institutional change that further fostered
growth. More generally, the system had lasting implications on the European
trajectory of contractual, organizational, legal and political developments."
(http://www.stanford.edu/~avner/Greif_Papers/2006%20JEP%20The%20Birth%20of%20Impersonal%20Exchange.pdf)

